@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{ "username": "{{username}}", "password": "{{password}}" }

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取组件注册表（默认 web 渲染器）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/components/registry
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 指定 mini-wx 渲染器
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/components/registry?renderer=mini-wx
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置租户级覆盖：隐藏 Chart 组件
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/components/overrides
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "type": "Chart",
  "hidden": true,
  "defaultPropsJson": null
}

### 取消覆盖
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/components/overrides/Chart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
